    <h1 class="opener__hed  -is-over-bg opener__hed--dark opener__hed--small" >        When Railroad Workers Get Hurt on the Job, Some Supervisors Go to Extremes to Keep It Quiet
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--dark">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
