rue_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1334&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=6a5529b3d4080ad4b9ea91c20f468b0c 2000w"
